'''''In Search Of Voodoo: Roots To Heaven''''' ni film ya documentaire ya biografiya yo muri [[Bene|Bénine]] 2018 iyobowe numukinnyi wamamaye wa Hollywood uzwi cyane Djimon Hounsou kandi afatanije numuyobozi ubwe hamwe na Eric McGaw. 

Iyi filime ishingiye ku bintu byabayeho mu buzima bwumukinnyi Djimon Hounsou kandi yibanda ku nkuru z’umuntu ku giti cye, umuco, ndetse n’umwuka za Voodoo, muri [[Afurika]] y’iburengerazuba.  Filime yakiriwe neza nabayireba. 

